${BOLD}Usage:${RESET} n0dm <command> [options]

${BOLD}Enhanced Commands (N0DM specific):${RESET}
  sync [message]            Safe sync with SMART backup: pull → commit → push
  backup [label]            Create manual backup of tracked files
  restore <id>              Restore from n0dm backup (use 'backups' to see IDs)
  backups                   List available n0dm backups
  cleanup                   Remove old backups per retention policy
  conflicts                 Check for unresolved merge conflicts
  status                    Show yadm status + n0dm backup info
  connect [repo]            Connect to GitHub remote (e.g., user/repo)
